Class DQAssessment

  • java.lang.Object
    • JenaDQ.DQAssessment

  • public class DQAssessment
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates and handle the Assessments. An assessment is composed by a target URI, a List of DQDimensions and an endpoint.
